{"tid":1652823,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"煩緊眼罩嘅手足同和理非同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-13T22:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:46:54.000Z","uid":273185,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edd0ec7ad6d3c0d7f6121a74229cc16f9cfb8df6","tid":1652823,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:15:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">見到依家仲有好多手足仲用緊泳鏡<br />\n因為氣密眼罩難入手,又未必啱面型,價錢仲要偏高,萬一要棄裝就好肉赤。相反泳鏡易入手,一定啱面型,價錢就有高有低,但勝在唔洗棄</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係小弟我自己都有用過泳鏡,戴住之後視野會有都幾多嘅限制,仲要勁唔舒服 戴耐咗真係勁想除</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">亦都相信在座唔少嘅和理非無力感都非常之重,次次出黎行完都好似無咩用咁,想幫前線出一分力又無咁嘅勇氣,個個都買水比前線但係又次次都派唔哂,氣密眼罩/豬咀又搵唔到方法入手或者負擔唔起</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">於是我參考咗之前一啲手足嘅方法,整咗個平靚正嘅整合版出黎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">就係普通眼罩+電線膠紙+3M海綿膠條</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcO0iON.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcO0iON.png&h=dfee1efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pq5BBAx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpq5BBAx.png&h=8b930144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLQub8Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLQub8Y.png&h=3a006129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">打War game嘅時候用都係比較舒服,視野亦無太多嘅限制<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正因為乜都無,所以乜都改到</span> 你可以用埋防霧筆,反光紙張佢改到啱自己心水</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">之前都有聽過同睇過有手足教過類似方法,但係又好似唔普遍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">製作成本非常之低,呢到總成本都係60蚊有找</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">眼罩$1X-2X<br />\n電線膠紙$X<br />\n3M海綿膠條$3X-4X</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其中電線膠紙同膠條都好大卷,可以整到10副左右.成本效益都可以話係唔錯</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位買夠10副眼罩嘅成本都只係$250內嘅事,夾埋幾個fd除返開仲平過你去食餐好嘅,所以有能力嘅絕對可以整比有需要嘅手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">除非閣下真係餐搵餐食</span>,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔係都唔好再搵d咩藉口去唔support前線,支持唔係口講就夠.就好似你阿媽都好愛你,咁可唔可以唔比零用錢你</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其次佢地嘅入手程度亦都相當容易,眼罩只係最普遍嘅1621,大部分五金鋪都好大機會會有,而電線膠紙亦都係五金鋪搵到,去到問佢有無黑色電線膠紙就得,但係你想要其他色都可以嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而最後嘅海綿膠條可以係日本城到搵到.可以話係邊到都可以買齊到</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當然到最後,亦最關心嘅一定係你講咁耐到底做唔做到氣密<br />\n<br />\n我測試過係<span style=\"color: red;\">完全唔入水</span>,就算你見我鼻位痴得咁樣衰都無事,黎緊打war game有煙就會去試下,麻煩各位巴絲打唔好相認</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同埋緊記呢個只係一個退而求其次嘅方法,如果可以嘅話 我都係建議大家用氣密眼罩</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">另外各位巴絲打有咩意見都可以交流改善下</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">各位手足如果覺得ok就麻煩幫手推下,P牌仔推唔到</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">PS:戴眼鏡會令則邊有罅</span></span>"},{"pid":"48e3f7ac9f6fe3a8ea10c01fde8b80a9cccd5e38","tid":1652823,"uid":54392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"fda78042e448db5fd6fc2a32aa9dee9e4e777c3d","tid":1652823,"uid":164688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未瞓幫你推"},{"pid":"d59d5477cd0e186cee3497a13bb931c07b089c75","tid":1652823,"uid":143171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:31:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecec76e3174d4ad2096b1f0149234a198994f6ea","tid":1652823,"uid":316672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd0ec7ad6d3c0d7f6121a74229cc16f9cfb8df6","tid":1652823,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:15:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">見到依家仲有好多手足仲用緊泳鏡<br />\n因為氣密眼罩難入手,又未必啱面型,價錢仲要偏高,萬一要棄裝就好肉赤。相反泳鏡易入手,一定啱面型,價錢就有高有低,但勝在唔洗棄</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係小弟我自己都有用過泳鏡,戴住之後視野會有都幾多嘅限制,仲要勁唔舒服 戴耐咗真係勁想除</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">亦都相信在座唔少嘅和理非無力感都非常之重,次次出黎行完都好似無咩用咁,想幫前線出一分力又無咁嘅勇氣,個個都買水比前線但係又次次都派唔哂,氣密眼罩/豬咀又搵唔到方法入手或者負擔唔起</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" 