r />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位買夠10副眼罩嘅成本都只係$250內嘅事,夾埋幾個fd除返開仲平過你去食餐好嘅,所以有能力嘅絕對可以整比有需要嘅手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">除非閣下真係餐搵餐食</span>,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔係都唔好再搵d咩藉口去唔support前線,支持唔係口講就夠.就好似你阿媽都好愛你,咁可唔可以唔比零用錢你</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其次佢地嘅入手程度亦都相當容易,眼罩只係最普遍嘅1621,大部分五金鋪都好大機會會有,而電線膠紙亦都係五金鋪搵到,去到問佢有無黑色電線膠紙就得,但係你想要其他色都可以嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而最後嘅海綿膠條可以係日本城到搵到.可以話係邊到都可以買齊到</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當然到最後,亦最關心嘅一定係你講咁耐到底做唔做到氣密<br />\n<br />\n我測試過係<span style=\"color: red;\">完全唔入水</span>,就算你見我鼻位痴得咁樣衰都無事,黎緊打war game有煙就會去試下,麻煩各位巴絲打唔好相認</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同埋緊記呢個只係一個退而求其次嘅方法,如果可以嘅話 我都係建議大家用氣密眼罩</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">另外各位巴絲打有咩意見都可以交流改善下</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">各位手足如果覺得ok就麻煩幫手推下,P牌仔推唔到</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">PS:戴眼鏡會令則邊有罅</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬好QQ"},{"pid":"50327f4a726063e44382c65a634e891bec1a273c","tid":1652823,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"邊到仲有人用呢啲眼罩 爆硬眼咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6beebc6dfbc1eec9b4968113faca5513d4f5fb2a","tid":1652823,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50327f4a726063e44382c65a634e891bec1a273c","tid":1652823,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"邊到仲有人用呢啲眼罩 爆硬眼咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"好過無"},{"pid":"34127efa7f2b9b64fdb9672d82e6df71b02858a9","tid":1652823,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50327f4a726063e44382c65a634e891bec1a273c","tid":1652823,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"邊到仲有人用呢啲眼罩 爆硬眼咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"仲有手足仲用緊泳鏡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋呢d就自己諗啦 如果只係做魔法師企得無咁前,我又覺得可以接受 同埋都話左係退而求其次嘅方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed3344dfc28c24773047674c12e464d90c02099","tid":1652823,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34127efa7f2b9b64fdb9672d82e6df71b02858a9","tid":1652823,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50327f4a726063e44382c65a634e891bec1a273c","tid":1652823,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"邊到仲有人用呢啲眼罩 爆硬眼咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"仲有手足仲用緊泳鏡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋呢d就自己諗啦 如果只係做魔法師企得無咁前,我又覺得可以接受 同埋都話左係退而求其次嘅方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"坊間咁撚多捐物資 肯主動問 要個眼罩一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1a1032e18f28d55d29fe9d6969078f36ecf9e1","tid":1652823,"uid":295011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"推行動post<br />\n緊急要人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac